itial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:left;\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;\">把这个风格打包成了一个为你的文章生成配图和封面的 Skills。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 0.9em;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这也是我为自己做的内容生产 Skills 系统中的一部分。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 0.9em;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">所以这篇内容</span></span><strong style=\"margin:0px;font-weight:600;box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">既有图片提示词也有 Skills</span></strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">，你可以选择自己喜欢的方式使用。</span></span></p>\n  <figure style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:1em 0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100011798\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border: 1px solid rgb(226, 232, 240);max-width: 100%;height: auto;margin: 0px auto;display: block;\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e03f45b8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FfbRX0iaT8Egfeicmn0GLDxUvmJPr4CSMT807fEp5L1wBiaarFHz1E8rrnDOXmUg3Tp17b9pK3becIDNa8iaYhyia9xw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n  </figure>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 0.9em;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">这个 Skills 具体的功能有：</span></span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 0.9em;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:1.6em;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;list-style-type:disc;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:left;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 0px 0.2em;\">\n    <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">支持分析当前文件夹下的任何格式文档,批量为每部分生成图片</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 0px 0.2em;\">\n    <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">支持选择图片生成的分辨率 2K、4K</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 0px 0.2em;\">\n    <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">支持选择图片生成的比例(16:9、3:4)</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 0px 0.2em;\">\n    <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">支持选择是否生成总结性质的封面图片</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 0px 0.2em;\">\n    <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">展示归纳结果供你确认,确保所有重要信息都被包含</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 0.9em;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">比如我前几天分享的 Cursor 关于 AI 编程概念的文章配图就是用这个生成的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 0.9em;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">简直是发小红书、微信图文、抖音图文的神器!</span></span></p>\n  <figure style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:1em 0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100011794\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border: 1px solid rgb(226, 232, 240);max-width: 100%;height: auto;margin: 0px auto;display: block;\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=01a82a5c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FfbRX0iaT8Egfeicmn0GLDxUvmJPr4CSMT82icMHY9ex2OTjpKlbAEfrMxO0pLiaxUFiazjVgmHG5RL5VZBrFbicprODg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n  </figure>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 0.9em;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">目前 Skills 里面内置了三套风格：</span></span><strong style=\"margin:0px;font-weight:600;box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">票据风格、矢量插画风格、渐变玻璃卡片风格。</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 0.9em;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">大家可以按照自己的喜好让模型生成对应风格的图片。</span></span></p>\n  <figure style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:1em 0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100011795\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border: 1px solid rgb(226, 232, 240);max-width: 100%;height: auto;margin: 0px auto;display: block;\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8f21a94d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FfbRX0iaT8Egfeicmn0GLDxUvmJPr4CSMT81MTRCUp5QgBonCvkyO0btRBjibFbAoibjgodRK3eNjVsqycfJOZgjQ4A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n  </figure>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 0.9em;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">接下来说一下怎么用。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 0.9em;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">你可以直接打开终端输入这段代码然后回车就行,他会自动安装。</span></span></p>\n  <pre style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;border-image:initial;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;overflow-x:auto;border-width:3px 1px 1px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;border-style:solid;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0.875em 1em;margin:1em 0px;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration-style:initial;border-color:rgb(59, 130, 246) rgb(226, 232, 240) rgb(226, 232, 240);font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><code style=\"border:none;padding:0px;margin:0px;display:block;overflow-x:auto;font-size:0.875em;font-family:&quot;SF Mono&quot;, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, monospace;line-height:1.5;box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">npx skills add <a href=\"https://github.com/op7418/Document-illustrator-skill\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/op7418/Document-illustrator-skill</a></span></code></pre>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 0.9em;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">安装完成之后你需要跟着 AI 的引导在 .env 文件里面填写你的 AI Studio API Key。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 0.9em;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这里获取 API Key：aistudio.google.com/api-keys</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 0.9em;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">因为调用的 Nano Banana Pro,所以你的 API 需要开启付费哈。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 0.9em;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">之后就在 Claude Code 里面跟他聊天就行：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 0.9em;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:left;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;font-style: italic;\"><span leaf=\"\">\"帮我用 /document-illustrator 这个Skills为 @\"文档名称\" 这个文档生成配图\"</span></em></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 0.9em;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0p