ev/img-proxy/?k=92493ee0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FfbRX0iaT8Egfeicmn0GLDxUvmJPr4CSMT8qyaCricfHwticYnPvpPV8Qso5phiaznImNyxLjJSESmBIfnQpGkxWm24g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n  </figure>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 0.9em;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">当然你要说我实在是不想用这个 Skills,我想要从自己的的渠道生成图片。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 0.9em;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">也可以的,直接从下面这里</span></span><strong style=\"margin:0px;font-weight:600;box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">复制提示词</span></strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">使用,其实就是我在去年三月发的给模型写代码的提示词。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 0.9em;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">然后图片生成也可以用，这里可以看到 Nano Banana Pro 这模型有多强大。</span></span></p>\n  <pre style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;border-image:initial;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;overflow-x:auto;border-width:3px 1px 1px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;border-style:solid;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0.875em 1em;margin:1em 0px;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration-style:initial;border-color:rgb(59, 130, 246) rgb(226, 232, 240) rgb(226, 232, 240);font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><code style=\"border:none;padding:0px;margin:0px;display:block;overflow-x:auto;font-size:0.875em;font-family:&quot;SF Mono&quot;, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, monospace;line-height:1.5;box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">帮我根据下面的设计风格要求和内容要求,生成一张中文的封面海报,不要有大段文字：</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">设计风格要求：</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">运用3-4种不同字号创造层次感,关键词使用最大字号</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">主标题字号需要比副标题和介绍大三倍以上,采用网格排版,类似高级杂志</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">文字与装饰元素间保持和谐的比例关系</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">确保视觉流向清晰,引导读者目光移动</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">数字极简票券风设计风格</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">黑白对比主导：高度对比的黑白配色方案,形成强烈视觉冲击</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">票券化布局：类似登机牌、门票或电子凭证的结构设计</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">几何分区明确：画面被精确划分为信息区块,井然有序</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">留白艺术运用：大量有效留白提升整体通透感和优雅度</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">东西方美学融合：结合中文传统排版与西方现代设计语言</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">工业设计感：注册商标符号、条形码等商业元素的精致运用</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">数字界面映射：模拟电子屏幕或应用界面的信息呈现方式</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">文字排版风格</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">中英混排对比：中英文字体混合使用,创造文化融合感</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">尺寸层级分明：主标题大号处理,副文本精致小巧</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">多向排列组合：包含横排、竖排、斜排等多方向文字布局</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">间距精确控制：字符间距和行距经过精心计算,保持呼吸感</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">符号化装饰：括号、下划线、箭头融入文字设计</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">衬线与非衬线混搭：不同字体家族交替使用,增强层次感</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">时间信息格式化：日期标注采用统一格式,搭配方向指示符</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">视觉元素风格</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">功能性指示符：各类箭头、星号作为视觉引导和强调</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">UI元素借鉴：\"CHECK IN\"、\"@\"等数字界面元素的平面化应用</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">边框与分割线：简洁线条用于区隔不同信息区域</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">简约图形符号：最小化的设计符号传达核心信息</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">手写风点缀：如\"Romantic\"的手写体为机械排版增添人文温度</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">方向性视觉流动：通过元素排布创造从左到右、从上到下的阅读节奏</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">负空间利用：将空白区域视为积极设计元素的一部分</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">文案内容为：[在这里填写你的文案或者标题]</span></code></pre>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 0.9em;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">好了,这就是今天的内容。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 0.9em;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果你感兴趣的话,也可以直接访问这个 GitHub (</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://github.com/op7418/Document-illustrator-skill\" target=\"_blank\">https:/